text: Toyoshimizu Station is a railway station located in Shimizu (清水), Bifuka, Nakagawa District (Teshio), Hokkaidō, and is operated by the Hokkaido Railway Company. ==Lines serviced== *Hokkaido Railway Company :*Sōya Main Line ==Adjacent stations== ==External links== *Ekikara Time Table - JR Toyoshimizu Station Category:Railway stations in Hokkaido Prefecture Category:Railway stations in Japan opened in 1950
